#Install and configure the Git in the CentOs7 #

Step01:

Install the git packages: 

# sudo yum install git

Step 02:

Verify the git Installated successfully or not :

# git --version

Step03:

Its madatory to add the personal information (such as your name,email ..etc):

# git config --global user.name "Your Name"
# git config --global user.email "emailaddress@domain.com"

Step04:

To verify the above configuration changes:

# git config --list

configuration settings are  stored in the ~/.gitconfig file

# cat ~/.gitconfig


